    <has_dmc>No</has_dmc>
  </oversight_info>
  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to determine if exenatide will improve global cardiac function
      in patients with type 2 diabetes mellitus and congestive heart failure, by favorable effects
      on cardiac metabolism leading to improvement of cardiac efficiency.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
